This constructor starts SHOP2 (unless it is already running), and then loads the specified domain file, and then it has SHOP2 create a plan for the specified task in the specified state.

This constructor starts SHOP2 (unless it is already running), and then loads the specified domain file and problem file, and then it has SHOP2 solve all of the problems that are defined in the problem file (printing the results as it goes).
